text:
Photo: Michael Macor, The Chronicle The Navy Blue Angels fly past the steeple of St. Peter and Paul Church as they take to the skies over San Francisco Bay during Fleet Week in San Francisco , Calif., on Sat. October 10, 2015. The Navy Blue Angels fly past the steeple of St. Peter and Paul...
This week the Bay Area was full of visitors with the Blue Angels flying overhead, Fleet Week in full swing and the hundreds of Corgis who decended on Ocean Beach for San Francisco’s Corgi Con Saturday.
